+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0
+
+/*
+ * Irqdomain for Linux to run as the root partition on Microsoft Hypervisor.
+ *
+ * Authors:
+ *  Sunil Muthuswamy <sunilmut@microsoft.com>
+ *  Wei Liu <wei.liu@kernel.org>
